 to detect React JSX and TSX files
*.jsx linguist-language=JavaScript
*.tsx linguist-language=TypeScript

# 2. Make sure React-related web files are counted
*.html linguist-detectable=true
*.css linguist-detectable=true

# 3. Exclude "noise" so your code percentage increases
# (This ignores the build folder if you accidentally committed it)
build/* linguist-vendored
dist/* linguist-vendored
